Package userProfile

Class UserProfile

java.lang.Object
userProfile.UserProfile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UserProfile extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a user profile with a name and type (e.g., ADULT, CHILD). Each profile is associated with a ProfileType, where we will have restrictions for the CHILD type. This class implements Serializable to support saving profiles as serialized objects.
Author:
Trudy Ann Roberts
